title: Among Us Nugget
author: Flan & Sofi
pages:
AMONG US NUGGET

In 2022, the chilean
chicken brand Super
Pollo announced their
official partnership
with the game Among
Us, launching a line of
special Crewmate-
shaped chicken
nuggets, only
available for a limited
time.
                        ->

To advertise this
collaboration, they
actually sent one of
these nuggets to
space using a weather
balloon, and
transmitted its ascent
on Twitch, but
unfortunately the
balloon popped after
only making it about
halfway to outer
space.
                        ->

PD: Never bought them
tho, but I've heard
they're pretty tasty-F

I did try them, they
were just nuggets,
but at least it was a
fun evening with
friends-S
